The paper presents a method for distributed reinforcement learning in simulated environments, specifically for training virtual robots to navigate in Habitat-Sim. This involves using deep learning techniques for scene understanding and navigation policies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
